The state capture Inquiry has heard explosive testimony of bribery involving Transnet Executives. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The state capture Inquiry has heard explosive testimony of bribery involving Transnet executives. Three unnamed witnesses testified via audio link. READ: Mokonyane: Agrizzi hates women Among the people implicated were Brian Molefe, Siyabonga Gama, Melusi Gigaba and Anoj Singh. The witnesses told the inquiry of bags of money allegedly coming from the Gupta residence.